{"tid":1876634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】有進展！HKTVmall再掃口罩濾網 夠做100萬口罩","createTime":"2020-02-12T13:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T14:24:44.000Z","uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5bce0c5bc9708916bcd3d995b906fdd5db0c5d9b","tid":1876634,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200212/large/1581509639_5eb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200212%2Flarge%2F1581509639_5eb0.jpg&h=86191d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHKTVmall於Facebook表示已買入口罩濾網，足夠生產100萬個口罩（圖片來源：HKTVmall Facebook）<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n【新增內容】<br />\nHKTVmall早前於台灣以20萬美元訂購口罩機，今日再於Facebook表示已買入口罩濾網，足夠生產100萬個口罩。<br />\nHKTVmall Facebook表示：「首先解說一下：一個口罩有三層構造，外層係防水不織布，阻隔飛沫同大粒粉塵；裡面嗰層係另一種比較柔軟嘅不織布，吸水並令面部皮膚更舒適。而最重要亦係最難訂嘅係中間嗰層Filter，作為屏障阻擋病菌。而今日R小隊有：重、大、進、展！最重要嗰層Filter已經到貨啦！足夠整超過一百萬個口罩！距離香港製造口罩又行近一大步！」<br />\n【下午4時38分】<br />\n香港電視（1137）旗下HKTVmall早前公佈一月平均每日訂單大按年大增65% ，並預期增長動力延至2月。在訂單急增的情況下，集團今日公佈2月短期上調會員免運費金額，為本月以為第二次調整。<br />\nHKTVmall在網上公佈，2月短期調整會員免運費金額。由明日（13日）凌晨至3月前，連續17日調整免運費金額，普通會員由400元上調至800元；VIP會員由400元上調至800元；門市自取維持200元。未買滿以上指定金額，運費劃一調整為80元。<br />\n公司表示，希望是次的短期改動可以減輕派送團隊的壓力，使物流和派貨部處理積壓的訂單，並指劃一會員免運費金額，是希望所有新舊客戶均可使用公司服務，縮短大家輪候派送的時間。<br />\n上一輪調整為本月4日起，普通會員購物滿500元方免運費、VIP會員則為350元；門市自取則為200元。<br />\n港視在預告會考慮融資活動後，即於昨晚宣佈配股，公司以先舊後新方式配售8000萬股，股份最終以下限定價5.15元，較昨日收市價折讓14.3%，公司股份今早受壓，雖然一度低見5.17元，但未曾跌穿配售價，股價收市報5.2元，跌13.48%，成交9.55億元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200212/large/1581509639_c819.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200212%2Flarge%2F1581509639_c819.jpg&h=0e686132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200212/large/1581509649_e7b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200212%2Flarge%2F1581509649_e7b9.jpg&h=39c4278f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200212/large/1581495732_5cfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200212%2Flarge%2F1581495732_5cfc.jpg&h=7ab64de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200212/large/1581496453_3487.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200212%2Flarge%2F1581496453_3487.png&h=c24b39e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200212/UQ4BMTM2HNW3VYECUNLB6UFVQM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200212%2FUQ4BMTM2HNW3VYECUNLB6UFVQM&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=ec7b8e54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200212%2FUQ4BMTM2HNW3VYECUNLB6UFVQM&h=94e1592f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200212/UQ4BMTM2HNW3VYECUNLB6UFVQM</a>"},{"pid":"0e8dc932f07054fbbf00f1e91bbc024f68dd7150","tid":1876634,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"800咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實勁多人買，做唔做得切？"},{"pid":"0567a612fadf264b3593eab32ddce575e75fd883","tid":1876634,"uid":123308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:52:07.000Z","msg":"錢唔係問題，問題係，而家入面好多糧食都冇貨，<br />\n點上到 $800 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再者，明白而家非常時期，真係做死物流，<br />\n但普通一般街客同 VIP 竟然係同級劃一 $800 免運費，<br />\n咁你個 VIP 要嚟做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n$600 都話可以理解<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：啱啱尋日買咗 $1000+ 嘢"},{"pid":"c086e25f3c770c6ab04e3839c93dfd2fc6a98b7d","tid":1